# Opdex Core Contracts

Core Opdex exchange contracts. Consists of a single deployable Controller contract and individual Pool contracts deployable from within. Pool types that can be created include Standard and Staking options.

- [Opdex Controller Contract](/docs/OpdexControllerContract.md)
- [Opdex Staking Pool Contract](/docs/OpdexStakingPoolContract.md)
- [Opdex Standard Pool Contract](/docs/OpdexStandardPoolContract.md)
- [Opdex Liquidity Pool Token Contract](/docs/OpdexLiquidityPoolTokenContract.md)

## Deploy

Use the provided bytecode to deploy the controller contract used to create and deploy liquidity pool contracts.

### Parameters
`Address stakingToken` - The address of token that will be used for staking in staking pools.
